message.content: {"name":"Science Fair","date":"Friday","location":{"city":"Springfield","state":"Illinois","country":"United States"},"activities":[{"activityName":"Rocket Launch Demonstration","description":"Witness an exhilarating live demonstration of model rockets being launched into the sky, performed by members of the Springfield Astronomical Society.","duration":"1 hour"},{"activityName":"Physics Puzzle Workshop","description":"Participants collaborate to solve engaging physics puzzles that challenge their understanding of mechanics and thermodynamics.","duration":"30 minutes"},{"activityName":"Science Trivia Contest","description":"Test your science knowledge and compete for prizes in a fun and interactive trivia game.","duration":"45 minutes"},{"activityName":"Biology Station Exploration","description":"Explore various hands-on exhibits related to biology, including microscope work and ecosystem models.","duration":"2 hours"}]}
